
### 3. .gitignore
Create a `.gitignore` file to exclude unnecessary files from your Git repository:

```gitignore
# Compiled source
*.abi
*.bin
*.hex

# Remix files
remix-ide

# Node modules
node_modules

# MacOS
.DS_Store

# Logs
*.log

# Coverage directory used by tools like istanbul
coverage
coverage.json

# Truffle build directory
build

# dotenv environment variables file
.env
